__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
dist/
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
AGENTS.md

# Local security-scan artifacts (Bandit/ZAP/Nikto/Nuclei/Wapiti bundles).
# Kept on disk for the operator, never tracked.
scan-*.tar.gz
scan-*/

# Local-only AI-assistant working notes — kept on disk for the agent to read,
# but never tracked, so they don't mirror to the production repo or releases.
# opencode.md is the OpenCode twin of CLAUDE.md and carries the same internal
# operational guidance, so it gets the same treatment (it was previously tracked
# by oversight — untracked in the v5.5.0 sweep).
CLAUDE.md
opencode.md

# Cursor rules imported from CLAUDE.md — same internal-only treatment
.cursor/

# Marketing landing page for remotepower.tvipper.com — a standalone deployable
# kept on disk but untracked, so it never reaches the production repo. Deploy it
# by copying site/ to that host's web root.
site/

# Environment-specific nginx deployment configs (real hostnames, cert paths,
# and the fw_private_rp IP allowlist for the PRIVATE vhost). Kept on disk for
# the operator but NEVER tracked — the public/shippable templates live in
# server/conf/ and docker/ instead.
deploy/

# Internal planning / roadmap / scoping notes — kept on disk for the agent and
# operator, never tracked, so they never reach the public/production repo.
docs/*-internal.md

# Local CodeQL scan cache (bundle + DBs + SARIF) — see tools/codeql-local.sh
.codeql-cache/

# Local design scratch / mockups — never published
design/

# Stray screenshots dropped in the repo root (use docs/screenshots/ for real ones)
/Screenshot_*.png
/*.png

# stray openclaw "dreaming" agent artifacts — never ship
DREAMS.md
memory/
openclaw-workspace-state.json

# openclaw/opencode agent scaffolding — internal AI-agent persona/workspace
# files, never product content; must never ship in the repo or tarball.
/AGENTS.md
/USER.md
/TOOLS.md
/SOUL.md
/IDENTITY.md
/HEARTBEAT.md
/BOOTSTRAP.md
/MEMORY.md

# Test-suite artifact: the Windows agent test writes its literal C:\ProgramData
# log path as a relative file on Linux. Never commit it.
C:*

# pre-release push stamp + CI-parity artifacts (local gate state, never shipped)
.pre-release-ok
.promote-state
.ci-parity-run.log
.ci-parity-venv/
.pre-release-run.log
.testfast-run.log
